00:18:06.002 --> 00:18:08.254
- Ngapain juga aku harus sopan sama dia, hah?
- Taehoon! Jangan!

00:18:08.337 --> 00:18:10.006
Sadarlah, bocah nakal.

00:18:13.843 --> 00:18:15.344
Ayo pergi, Sangyeol.

